Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:47.95,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,1996年10月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:54.98,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,来到火星的我们 被卷入了未知战斗兵器的战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:57.57,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,基地被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:03.45,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,活下来的只剩下我们这些人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:05.56,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.53,0:02:08.32,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:15.78,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我的名字叫英二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.58,0:02:17.94,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,地球被盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:23.56,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760)}他的名字叫英二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:25.44,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我的名字叫英二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:27.50,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,地球被盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.10,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我是来告诉你们这个情报的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:30.08,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.19,0:02:34.73,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,你是苏联军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.02,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,还是美军
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.83,0:02:40.73,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,刚才是怎么回事 为什么把我们卷入战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:42.73,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我是从古拉多斯来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:44.78,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,是位于于乌多利亚太阳系的行星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:48.44,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了 你是想耍我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:52.80,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,你驾驶的那架机体是什么 看起来像是秘密开发的战斗兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:55.07,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我是从古拉多斯来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:03:00.18,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,你以为我们会相信你的鬼话吗 你的上级是谁 我们要把你关起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:06.01,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,这时候 我们还没搞清楚到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:12.05,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,眼前发生的事太过突然 我们完全来不及思考
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:31.88,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:56.23,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.31,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.32,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:19.09,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,雷 报告目前的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.09,0:04:21.54,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,有三艘太空船侵入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:22.45,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,预计接触时间是多少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:24.37,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,5±1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:25.79,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,剩余能量还有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.79,0:04:28.98,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,预计可行动时间 46±5
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:30.75,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,全速回避
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:34.76,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,被敌人探测器侦测到的概率在90%以上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:36.64,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,这就够了 要的就是这个效果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:40.99,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,重复 探测到敌人的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:44.30,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我不想把地球人卷入到战斗中 我要马上离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:45.31,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,进行地形分析
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.31,0:04:45.91,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,已就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.26,0:05:22.76,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,看 和之前一样的战斗兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:31.83,Default_Sub,Man 2,0,0,0,,战斗机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:35.58,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,果然是苏联和美国在交战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:39.05,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了 怎么会在这种时候开战
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:40.70,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,不要做毫无根据的推论
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:44.88,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,我也觉得不太可能 但确实已经露出了战争的獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:51.38,Default_Sub,Man 2,0,0,0,,总之 肯定发生了什么严重的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:06:00.65,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,听好了 你们马上回房间去 一步也不要迈出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.31,0:06:03.96,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我们都能回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.40,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.40,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,好了 快点 小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:10.23,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,不用担心 跟着我就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:13.26,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,是啊 还真像个大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:26.56,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二 能听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:28.24,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:32.39,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二 乖乖投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:35.36,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,先不说古雷斯科舰队的名誉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:39.89,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,光是你窃夺SPT就已经是重罪了 而且你居然还向追踪部队开火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:42.26,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二 能听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:47.28,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,我是你的伙伴 我希望你能尽可能受到较轻的处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.92,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,回答我 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:51.91,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,抱歉 盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:54.13,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:57.06,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,和你说了这么多 还是不打算投降吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.18,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:58.98,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:00.77,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,理由是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:05.01,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,说不出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:07.69,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,成为古拉多斯的叛徒也没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.28,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二 这是最后的警告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:14.87,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,马上投降 否则我们就攻击了 给你十秒钟 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.55,0:07:20.66,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不能杀驾驶员 雷 调查下那类机甲的结构
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.53,Default_Sub,EijI,0,0,0,,攻击那里的话就能让它停止行动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:25.31,Default_Sub,EijI,0,0,0,,进入战斗模式 准备反击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:25.91,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,已就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:27.50,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,十秒到了 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:43.14,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,雷 分析地形 要准备战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:43.78,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,已就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:15.00,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,苏联军方 苏联军方 请回答 这里是联合国基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:19.23,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,美国军方 美国军方 这里是联合国基地 联合国基地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.33,0:08:25.36,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,可恶 不行 无论是美国基地还是苏联基地都完全无法联络
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.44,Default_Sub,Man 2,0,0,0,,迄今为止没发现有生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.91,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:31.15,Default_Sub,Man 3,0,0,0,,你们那里有什么进展
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:36.91,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,不行 噪音太大 我们可能遇到了干扰电波 我会再尝试联络的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:42.03,Default_Sub,Girl 1,0,0,0,,食物和水源没有问题 但是急需生命维持装置
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:46.70,Default_Sub,Girl 1,0,0,0,,虽然做了紧急维修 但是用于补充的零件全被吹走 没有剩余了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:48.14,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,还剩多少
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:51.69,Default_Sub,Girl 1,0,0,0,,氧气的话还能维持四五天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:53.69,Default_Sub,Girl 2,0,0,0,,只能请求救援了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:11.94,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,不要走来走去的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.63,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你这样让我更烦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.63,0:09:21.15,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,西蒙尼 不是只有你一人担心今后的情况 冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:25.43,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,越这样想就越冷静不下来 而且需要冷静的是亚瑟你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:26.59,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,西蒙尼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:30.18,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,真的爆发战争了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.18,0:09:32.78,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,刚才不是你说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:36.01,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,我只是说美苏是不是在交战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:40.48,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,都一样 我们不是看到三架美国战机被击落了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:42.16,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,你的意思是敌人是苏联吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:44.37,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,还有别的可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:49.85,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,那不还是说明两国在交战吗 这不就是一直在原地转圈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:50.51,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.30,0:09:56.39,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,那个人果然就是地球的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:58.73,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,安娜你该不会相信他编的那些话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:04.32,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,总之我们需要更多的情报 为了更清楚事情的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:06.11,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,去问问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.11,0:10:07.15,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:12.17,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,顺便找一下大卫吧 他不知道去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.72,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,你很在意那家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:16.72,Default_Sub,Simone,0,0,0,,他的脸色不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:23.16,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,苏联军方!  苏联军方!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:24.64,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:29.89,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,有干扰电波 也就是说还在战斗中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:35.07,Default_Sub,Woman 1,0,0,0,,也可能是两边的基地都被歼灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:39.62,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,我不是告诉你们不要离开房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:42.35,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我是亚瑟 我代表大家来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:46.32,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,我们有权知道到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:51.35,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,还有那个... 你也有告诉我们的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:55.10,Default_Sub,Man 2,0,0,0,,博士 能来一下8号门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.75,0:10:59.82,Default_Sub,Man 2,0,0,0,,您的学生 该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:13.83,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:21.46,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,大卫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:22.42,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,朱诺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.58,0:11:25.73,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,就在门的另一边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:29.52,Default_Sub,David,0,0,0,,他一定在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:32.00,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,朱诺他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:34.71,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,朱诺他一直和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:37.38,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,站起来到大家那里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:38.62,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:46.25,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,如果这是梦的话 请快点醒来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:52.06,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,在这段如同静止的痛苦时间里 我一直这样祈祷着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:59.11,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,如果这是梦的话 请快点醒来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:02.38,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我想大家一定也在这样祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:36.61,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,后方2-0位置请注意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.44,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,哪里被击中了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:45.99,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,左腕关节系统受损 二次回路开始运作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:35.11,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二 不要让我为难啊 你姐姐就要和我结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:37.03,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,你这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.03,0:13:39.83,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,丢掉30%的推进燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:42.45,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,警报 可视范围减小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.95,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,全部丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.95,0:13:44.43,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,已完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.20,0:13:51.07,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,启动雷达战斗系统
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.07,0:13:51.79,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,已就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:02.52,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,警报 后方有敌人追击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.65,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,启动ECM
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:04.08,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,已启动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:11.01,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:13.08,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,侦察系统失灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:17.46,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,利用这个机会 记忆系统启动 切换到自动操纵系统
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:18.00,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,已就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:31.31,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,警报 前方有障碍物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:58.93,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,根据我们掌握的事实情况分析 美苏两国应该处于交战状态
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.93,0:15:02.29,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,但是 我们还不能妄下定论
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:05.04,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,现在需要精准无误的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:10.67,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,我们现在就去美军基地 去取得完整的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:15.73,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,我们也会尽力让大家快点回去 请大家放心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.09,0:15:27.64,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,系统下线 系统下线
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.56,0:15:48.40,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二 躲起来也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:51.05,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,与我们为敌是没有胜算的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:55.62,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,你有没有想过 如果你姐姐知道她弟弟是叛徒会是什么感受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:59.10,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二 现在还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.24,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,快点投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:18.30,Default_Sub,Com,0,0,0,,消息 热能探测器有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.65,0:16:24.22,Default_Sub,Pilot A,0,0,0,,盖尔队长 地球人的基地探测到反应 好像还有生还者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.30,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,没有把他们全消灭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.14,Default_Sub,Pilot A,0,0,0,,属下愿意效劳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:27.80,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,全部消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:28.40,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:37.94,Default_Sub,Elizabeth,0,0,0,,大家快回地下室去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.74,0:16:45.02,Default_Sub,Pilot A,0,0,0,,看啊 惊慌的猴子们束手无策了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:47.68,Default_Sub,Pilot B,0,0,0,,一个也不要留 全部消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:54.83,Default_Sub,Roanne?,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:09.12,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,快到里面去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.06,Default_Sub,Man 1,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:11.40,Default_Sub,Roanne,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:11.92,Default_Sub,Arthur,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.51,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:49.29,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,你在干什么 你为什么要保护地球人的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:18:00.75,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,是吗 原来是这样 所以你才与我们为敌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:01.90,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,警报
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.90,0:18:03.01,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:05.18,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,正在被敌人瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:10.23,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,我忘了你体内有一半地球人的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:12.01,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,完全忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:13.98,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,必须马上转移目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:18.90,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,所以才会背叛古雷克斯舰队 窃夺SPT
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.99,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,请原谅我 盖尔前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:28.49,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,听清楚 英二 你的归属是古拉多斯 你是古拉多斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:31.82,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,我也一直把你当做古拉多斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:34.50,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,你为什么要站在地球人那边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:38.65,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,你是在古拉多斯长大的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.65,0:18:43.84,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,是古拉多斯的阳光 土地 还有空气把你养大的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.84,0:18:48.75,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,就算这样我身体里也有一半地球人的血统 爸爸是地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:52.20,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,警报 已被敌人瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:55.57,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,醒醒吧 英二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:57.98,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,必须马上转移目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:19:02.02,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,睁大你的眼睛看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:06.93,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,地球人的宇宙开拓计划只会成为动乱的根源 现在他们不正是这样在火星上建造基地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:11.20,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,就算这样 为什么要消灭地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:14.52,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,现在没时间和你争论 让开
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:16.52,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,警报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:19.19,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,把地球人的生还者全部消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:23.71,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不要 基地里面有和我一样的地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:28.24,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,已被敌人瞄准 必须马上转移目标
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:32.00,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,就算你说不要 我们也要执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:35.05,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,警报
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:36.05,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:57.50,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,把基地和地球人一起消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:19:59.67,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.56,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,请不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:20.54,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,警报 请马上离开瞄准区域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:21.84,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我不会离开的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:29.64,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,凭你的技术根本打不到我 你应该明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:33.49,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,手腕部受损
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:35.75,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,左脚能源回路受损
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.68,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,胸部通讯系统受损
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:41.54,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,损伤严重 请马上脱离战斗区域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:43.95,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不行 基地里还有地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:48.78,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,敌方瞄准目标变更为SPT中枢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:52.83,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,目标击破率在95%以上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:21:04.24,Default_Sub,Julia,0,0,0,,英二 说不定我们会结婚 当然还早得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.83,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,请马上进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.55,0:21:09.92,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,剩余时间15秒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:11.51,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,还有15秒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:12.19,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,14
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:13.20,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,13
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:14.11,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,12
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:14.97,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,11
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:15.97,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:17.02,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:17.99,Default_Sub_Top,Rey,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:18.29,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.99,0:21:18.90,Default_Sub_Top,Rey,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.90,0:21:20.01,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:20.63,Default_Sub,Rey,0,0,0,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:28.30,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,妈妈 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:37.14,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:42.35,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,盖尔前辈 要杀他们的话就请先杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:46.20,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,拜托了 要杀他们的话就先杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:51.84,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,我的体内和他们一样流着红色的血 请你看看 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:53.84,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,请先杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:03.09,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,停止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.04,0:22:10.25,Default_Sub,Eiji,0,0,0,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:16.11,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,英二 这下 我们已经走上了不同的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.11,0:22:19.14,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,下次再碰面我不会手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.14,0:22:20.00,Default_Sub,Gail,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:20.70,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:36.84,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,我 对于自己能够做到的事 简直像是梦一样难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:47.67,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,更令人难以置信的是 这位来自古拉多斯的少年 用自己的身体救了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.26,0:23:01.56,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,990)}那个人的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:06.34,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(729,990)}如果静静地凝视
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.23,0:23:13.70,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,990)}只要他在身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.86,0:23:19.68,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(730,990)}就会觉得安心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.90,0:23:25.73,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(700,990)}比起任何的 甜言蜜语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:32.90,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715,990)}我最喜欢的还是此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.71,0:23:39.55,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(735,990)}只要五分钟就好 让我尽情地说出一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:45.20,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(750,990)}不要再想别的了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.02,0:23:50.95,Layzner_OP&ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(713,990)}Don't say...Don't say...anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.74,0:23:59.41,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,你好像没有理解我的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.41,0:24:00.43,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.43,0:24:03.04,Default_Sub,Anna,0,0,0,,听我说
